# Case Study: 6774 – Date Parsing Failure in Payment Upload

## Context

This case study documents the analysis of a production Jira defect where a **Payment Upload workflow failed with a user-visible 500 error** when date values were provided as Excel serial numbers.

The Jira ticket lacked explicit acceptance criteria for handling numeric date formats and exposed ambiguity around expected user-visible behavior.

